title: War of the Roses: Twins That Are NOT Close
description: Morgan thinks her twin sister Maddie might be cheating on her Maddie's boyfriend Dalton.  Morgan saw something on Maddie's Snapchat that is causing her to be curious.  Morgan and Maddie are not that close and Morgan really likes Dalton so she does War of the Roses on her sister to figure out what's going on.
